Class PHDLDevice

java.lang.Object
  phdl.PHDLDevice

public class PHDLDevice
extends java.lang.Object

A class that represents a device definition on a PCB. Stores a name, a set of attributes, and a set of pins

Version:
0.1
Author:
Richard Black and Brad Riching
